14:32.254 --> 14:34.349
Sorry. I, uh... I geek out sometimes...

14:34.351 --> 14:36.227
well, a lot.

14:36.252 --> 14:38.286
And I still have bad intentions,

14:38.288 --> 14:39.883
but...

14:39.908 --> 14:41.643
I'm gonna recruit you, too.

14:41.668 --> 14:44.883
Ladies and gentlemen, Kyle
West and Megan Morrison.

14:48.064 --> 14:50.033
